Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_collec...traversal_mode(25.10)    timing_collec...traversal_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_collection_all_fanin_fanout_traversal_mode

Syntax
       timing_collection_all_fanin_fanout_traversal_mode {hierarchical | flat}

       Default: flat

       Controls     how     the    software    processes    netlists    during
       all_fanin/all_fanout command processing.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

